    "description": "Fiery Ruin: This psicrown has 750 power points. It is made from reddish iron and is shaped into a twisted circlet studded with reddish crystals. It allows use of the following powers. Energy ball Energy cone Energy missile Energy stun Fiery discorporation Strong psychokinesis; ML 15th; Craft Psicrown, energy ball , energy cone , energy missile , energy stun , fiery discorporation ; Price 67,500 gp.",
